summary:
CAPTAIN MARVEL #1
KELLY THOMPSON (W) • CARMEN CARNERO (A)
Cover by Amanda Conner & Paul Mounts
variant Cover by Alex...
body:
CAPTAIN MARVEL #1

KELLY THOMPSON (W) • CARMEN CARNERO (A)

Cover by Amanda Conner & Paul Mounts

variant Cover by Alex Ross

variant Cover by Lauren Tsai

variant Cover by Adam Hughes

VARIANT COVER BY JOE QUESADA

Movie variant cover also available

ALL THE STARS ALIGN AS KELLY THOMPSON AND CARMEN CARNERO TAKE ON MARVEL’S PREMIER FEMALE SUPER HERO!

As Captain Marvel, Carol Danvers has spent months in space protecting Earth from alien threats big and small, but now it’s time for Earth’s mightiest hero to come home. New York City has never looked so good. But every re-entry comes with the unexpected, and Carol is about to hit a whole lot of unexpected. It’s a fresh start and an oversized, star-studded welcome home for a hero who’s been punching the glass ceiling since the 1970s — and just in time for the first female-led film from Marvel Studios! The next 50 years of Captain Marvel starts here!

40 PGS./Rated T+ …$4.99

title: dating carol danvers headcanons (marvel)
body:
Request - None

(a/n): yeah, yeah, the movie isn’t out yet BUT there’s comics so I have sources. also expect more of these :)

  • She’s a huge dork.
  • Like, a big dork.
  • “Aw, do you liiikkkeee me?”
  • “We’re dating.”
  • “Still.”
  • She’s very protective.
  • But like, anyone takes one look at her and they bounce.
  • She’s an adrenaline junkie at heart.
  • So lots of amusement park dates.
  • She likes to take them for flights.
  • Sometimes with a plane, sometimes it’s her picking them up and literally taking them to the sky.
  • She lets them wear her suit and thinks they look adorable in it.
  • Not much of a cuddler, but she does like to hold their hand while they sleep.
  • Huge kisser, though.
  • Loves to kiss their lips, especially when she gets back from a mission.
  • She doesn’t even care who’s looking.
  • She just kisses without remorse.
  • Her kisses are amazing btw.
  • They’re gentle and pleasant, never too rough.
  • And her lips are pillow soft.
